'''奧維納維公司'''（{{lang-en|Ovintiv Inc.}}）是一家總部位於[[加拿大|加拿大]][[卡爾加里|卡爾加里]]的天然氣、石油生產商。它是加拿大最大的天然氣生產商之一，前身為「恩卡納公司」（{{lang-en|Encana Corporation}}）。<ref name=EncanaPetrochina>{{cite news
 |url         = http://www.china.ualberta.ca/en/In%20the%20News/2012/December/EncanasPetroChinaPartnershipMayBeFirstofMany.aspx
 |title       = Encanas PetroChina Partnership May Be First of Many
 |author      = Rebecca Penty
 |publisher   = China Institute, University of Alberta
 |location    = Edmonton, AB
 |date        = December 17, 2012
 |accessdate  = February 1, 2013
 |deadurl     = yes
 |archiveurl  = https://web.archive.org/web/20131203074120/http://www.china.ualberta.ca/en/In%20the%20News/2012/December/EncanasPetroChinaPartnershipMayBeFirstofMany.aspx
 |archivedate = 2013年12月3日
}}</ref>

2009年11月30日分成兩家公司，負責天然氣生產的仍然維持現名，負責石油的公司改名為[[Cenovus_Energy|Cenovus Energy]]。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.thestar.com/Business/article/424300 | work=The Star | location=Toronto | title=EnCana announces dividing into two companies | date=2008-05-11 | accessdate=2010-05-02 | archive-date=2012-10-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121015104228/http://www.thestar.com/Business/article/424300 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

